name: [Character] Hecate (Granblue Fantasy)
description:
Reference from Granblue Fantasy Character, Hecate.

Please read About This Version to understand the instruction and how each Model are behave.

To use Lora Model :
1. location to put the loRA data (stable-diffusion-webui\models\Lora).
2. In Stable Diffusion you can prompt for Lora list by press "<" and type the Lora name or go to show/hide extra network which is bottom of Generate button and refresh it.

modelVersions.description:
This is Collab version are train with very less source and parameters, thus it won't likely be as close as original Hecate 1.0v but you can get your fox girl image consistently in any Weight!.

Trigger Word Instruction:
-for Anime:
"orange eyes, blonde hair, fox ears, cat eyes, black dress, ahoge, ornaments, long hair, <lora:Hecate-01:1>"

-for Realistic:
"hecate, orange eyes, blonde hair, fox ears, cat eyes, black dress, ahoge, ornaments, long hair, <lora:Hecate-01:1>"

-for NSFW Add-On:
"naughty face, sexual suggestive"

Weight:
All weight is working well, is only depend to the checkpoint and try play around with clip skip.

some instruction need to be clear:
-This Model is heavily train as Anime Models
1.Most of Anime & Semi-Realistic Checkpoint shall work well with this model, a slightly adjust weight shall fix most of flaw without need quality prompt.
2.All prompt even NSFW should work with this model easily cause the Original Model is suppose to be a horny fox, lol.

-This Model have lot of flaw for Very Realistic Image.
1.The Model mostly has flaw when it come to realistic face, while other anatomy is seem to be fine.
2. using her trigger prompt "hecate" might solve and might not for some image.
3.Adetailer is extremely recommended for Realistic face fix, it work like a magic just by enable it.
